title: All Groups of Interest Listed by GoI Number (Fragment)
content:
[[collapsible show="▷ All Groups of Interest with a GoI Number" hide="◁ All Groups of Interest with a GoI Number"]]
The Foundation has encountered a wide range of different organisations. Many of these encounters are one-off occurrences, but extensive records are maintained to keep track of these Groups of Interest if they every show up again. 
This is an open collaboration, to list any GoI numbers you feel like adding, from any branch, with documentation of it being used. This is mostly just for reference.
